      "title": "Pregnancy TIFFA Scan for Twins – Level 2 Ultrasound at Cadabams Diagnostics",
      "description": "Discover how the specialized TIFFA scan for twins at Cadabams Diagnostics detects anomalies early, monitors growth discordance, and guides safe delivery. Book your Level 2 ultrasound today.",
